---
title: Lemon & Herb Chicken Strips with Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Zesty! Herby! Creamy! This Mediterranean-inspired meal features lemon, garlic and herbs in an easy marinade for chicken breast strips, while currants and carrot bring colour and flavour to the buttery couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-garlic-herb-chicken-7c995bf5.jpg
